The low voltage electrical supply for site supplies to connectable electrical installations shall be in accordance with:
(a) AS/NZS 3000; and
(b) the additional or modified requirements of this Standard; and
(c) other applicable Standards, including but not limited to:
(i) AS/NZS 4509 (all parts);
(ii) AS/NZS 3010;
(iii) AS/NZS 5033;
(iv) AS/NZS 4777 (all parts);
(v) AS/NZS 4763; and
(vi) AS/NZS 5139.
See Figure 2.1 for supply arrangements.
